OL,3,CWork restarts on Jersey Zoo's multi-
OL,4,Cmillion-pound gorilla house
OL,6,FWork has restarted on a new multi-
OL,7,Fmillion-pound gorilla house at Jersey
OL,8,FZoo.
OL,10,FIt is the second phase of development
OL,11,Fto create a better home for the site's
OL,12,Ffour gorillas, following delays due to
OL,13,Fincreasing material costs.
OL,15,FThe larger enclosure will feature a
OL,16,Fmodern heating and cooling system,
OL,17,Feight separate bedroom spaces and
OL,18,Ftraining and weighing areas.
