OL,3,CWork restarts on Jersey Zoo's multi-
OL,4,Cmillion-pound gorilla house
OL,6,FJersey Zoo's Team Leader for Apes,
OL,7,FMark Beresford, says: "For the public,
OL,8,Fit's going to be a much nicer viewing
OL,9,Farea and for the gorillas, it's a much
OL,10,Fnicer area.
OL,12,F"It should also be about four or five
OL,13,Ftimes as big on the inside."
OL,15,FGorillas have been at Jersey Zoo since
OL,16,F1959 and the current gorilla house was
OL,17,Fbuilt in 1981.
