OL,3,CWork restarts on Jersey Zoo's multi-
OL,4,Cmillion-pound gorilla house
OL,6,FThe zoo says the new building will
OL,7,Fbring a lot of improvements, including
OL,8,Fresearch balconies and a full CCTV
OL,9,Fsystem to monitor the great apes'
OL,10,Fbehaviours.
OL,12,FCurator of Mammals, Ben Matthews,
OL,13,Fsays: "The key features are a deep
OL,14,Fbark chip floor which will encourage
OL,15,Fnatural foraging behaviour and
OL,16,Fincrease the ambient humidity in the
OL,17,Fbuilding.
