OL,3,CWork restarts on Jersey Zoo's multi-
OL,4,Cmillion-pound gorilla house
OL,6,F"It's much taller, so we've got a new
OL,7,Fclimbing structure being built inside
OL,8,Fwith over 50 points at the top of the
OL,9,Fstructure to attach ropes and webbing.
OL,11,F"The key message is progress and we're
OL,12,Ftaking all the good stuff we've learnt
OL,13,Fand not just at Jersey but in the
OL,14,Fwider zoo community and putting that
OL,15,Finto practice for what will be a very
OL,16,Fexciting build."
OL,18,FThe cost of the new enclosure has not
OL,19,Fbeen disclosed but should be completed
OL,20,Fby the summer of 2025.
